      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCKY LINKS (4) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, finishing in the money last time when 2nd at this track over 320m. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. One of the leading chances. BUGATTI RICO (2) jumped from the rails and recorded an upset win in a Grade 5 last time, scoring by 1.3 lengths at this track (18.42). Has a good record here at this journey. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Bold showing expected again. BABETTE FUSION (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (18.93) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Expected to give a good account. IMPRESS ROUSEY (1) has to be respected despite coming off a five weeks break.",
